{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0fe83c22d4","title":"四平防御战不能成为一般作战方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08f69a1195","index":0,"year":1946,"month":5,"day":27,"articleId":"0fe83c22d4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4ea5bda1c9","type":"paragraph","text":"四平防御战不能成为一般作战方针！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0fe83c22d4"},{"id":"8793637272","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年5月27日）东北四平街之所以能久守，主要是因故未料我军有防线，故逐次增兵，便于为我各个击破，便故遗受我军重大打击。故四平防御战为一时特殊条件所致，不能成为我一般的作战方针。目前，我力守大城市则许多中、小城市将被丢掉，许多运动战各个击破敌人的机会不能利用，敌如继续增兵对我守军进行包围攻击，则我必然乃要放弃大城市。口这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致各战略区电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0fe83c22d4"}],"page":{"id":"e198372d06","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"0fe83c22d4","start":350,"end":350}}}},"__N_SSG":true}